headline: How The New Price Target Is Reshaping The Story For HP (HPQ)
summary: What the New Price Target Means for HP’s Story HP’s latest price target update reflects a fresh view on how the market is interpreting the company’s outlook, even though the specific figures behind that target shift are not provided here.
